arneson cassi kyle larsen zack leonard nathan hanson melissa wyatt kayleigh hannah joshua and madeline leonard  great grandchildren megan lauren kailyn and arianna sister patricia harry hardwick of jackson tn and  brothers john richard shirley leonard of fort smith ar and james velma leonard of jackson tn he was preceded in death by his parents wife donna and son philip leonard a funeral service will be held at  am on friday march   at schneider apfel schneider  schneider funeral home with msgr james uppena officiating interment will be in mt olivet cemetery a visitation will be held on friday from  to  am at schneider apfel schneider  schneider funeral home funeral home schneider apfel schneider  schneider funeral directors  e racine st janesville wi  email us profile of schneider apfel schneider  schneider funeral directors send flowers send condolences previous send flowerss send food plant a tree in the holy land send a personalized card plant a tree in the us make a donation send a soup gift basket create an oral history support library plant trees in israel memorial cards  bookmarks next search other sources visitation march    am to  am schneider apfel schneider  schneider funeral home  east racine street janesville wi    get directions schneider apfel schneider  schneider funeral home  east racine street janesville wi  visitation for thomas c leonard httpwwwtributescomobituaryshowthomascleonardservices httpwwwtributescomobituarygeticsservicetr funeral service march    am schneider apfel schneider  schneider funeral home  east racine street janesville wi    get directions schneider apfel schneider  schneider funeral home  east racine street janesville wi  funeral service for thomas c leonard httpwwwtributescomobituaryshowthomascleonardservices httpwwwtributescomobituarygeticsservicetr interment friday march   mt olivet cemetery  n washington st janesville wi    get directions mt olivet cemetery  n washington st janesville wi  interment for thomas c leonard ht